  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the claypot over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook until fragrant.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the beef brisket and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the red curry paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the beef broth, tomato paste, potatoes, and carrots.",
    "Bring the stew to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 2 hours.",
    "Stir in the chopped nuka pickle and season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
